<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The President may suspend the provisions of this subchapter during a national emergency.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id80b5ec09-3a70-11f1-b817-c08bf6d1fe2c">(<ref href="/us/pl/107/217">Pub. L. 107–217</ref>, <date date="2002-08-21">Aug. 21, 2002</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/116/1153">116 Stat. 1153</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
